column4:
Yes, I've heard the tale; 
you are heading to the new Ark 
that fell into the western sea, correct?

I'm going to Mergoda.
This isn't where I belong;
my place is over there!

I think it might be that she wanted a break,
or perhaps just some time alone;
something along the lines of that.

However, that is the way of nature. 
Back then, Lord White Dragon was nothing special;
but something akin to the wind and the clouds.

No, Mayleaf is safe;
she should be by 
Lord White Dragon's side.
